import "../styles/signup.css";
import {Container , Box , TextField,Link as MuiLink, Button, Typography} from "@mui/material";
import {Link} from "react-router-dom";

export default function Signup() {
  return (
    <Container className="signup-container" >
   <Box className="signup-box">
    <Typography className="signup-text" variant="h4">
        Register
    </Typography>
    <Box component="form" className="signup-field">
    <TextField 
              margin="normal" 
              variant="outlined"
              required
              fullWidth
              type="username"
              label="Username"
              id="username"/>
    <TextField 
              margin="normal" 
              variant="outlined"
              required
              fullWidth
              label="Email"
              id="email"/>
    <TextField 
              margin="normal" 
              variant="outlined"
              required
              fullWidth
              type="password"
              label="Password"
              id="password"/>
    <TextField 
              margin="normal" 
              variant="outlined"
              required
              fullWidth
              type="password"
              label="Confirm Password"
              id="password"/>

              <Button type="submit" className="signup-pad"
                variant="contained" style={{backgroundColor:'red'}}>Sign up</Button>
              <Button type="submit" className="signup-pad"
                variant="contained" style={{backgroundColor:'blue'}}>Sign up with google</Button>

            <MuiLink component={Link} className="signup-pad" to="signup">Already have an account?Click here</MuiLink>
              </Box>
   </Box>
   </Container>
  )
}
